    {
      "id": "1b44750c-f3ba-80da-8331-d923acb20ed2",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The authors explore this issue by forming 15 teams of 4 students and analyze their spacial and vocal engagements to find 2 distinct clusters who exhibited significant differences relative to a multinomial null model. ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "1b44750c-f3ba-80da-8331-d923acb20ed2",
        "parent": {
          "type": "page_id",
